metadata.name: Ticket for Korea Blockchain week
metadata.description:
Won this but I can't make it, so I'm selling the ticket cheaper than cost price to someone who can and as an experiment. 
Owning this NFT will provide you access to Korea Blockchain Week 2020-2021 /// To redeem your conference ticket, please email info@koreablockchainweek.com at least 30 days before KBW2020-2021 with your name and ETH address associated with this NFT. You will then transfer this NFT to the KBW public ETH address they provide to receive your free ticket coupon.
